------------------------------------------------------------
-- AO Counts in Snowflake by student enrollment
------------------------------------------------------------
select dc.campus_code, ao_code, count(distinct student_pidm) from test_refined.ods.ods_course_enrollment fce
join test_curated.edw.dim_course dc on dc.term_code = fce.term_code and dc.crn = fce.crn
where fce.term_code = '202403' and dc.campus_code = '6'
group by dc.campus_code, ao_code
order by count(distinct student_pidm) desc
;
 
------------------------------------------------------------
-- AO Counts in dsdmgr registration table
------------------------------------------------------------
select campus_code, academic_organization, count(distinct student_pidm)  from test_raw.dsdmgr.dsd_registration
where term_code = '202403' and campus_code = '6'
group by campus_code, academic_organization
order by count(distinct student_pidm) desc
